comment: Young hints of apricot, vanilla sugar cookie, and pepper. Finishes with rye spice and lingering heat.
Very smooth at first, with a strong bite.  A little bit sweet.
Strong on first taste, but mellows as you sip it. Blend of Small Batch Rye and Small Batch Bourbons. 80% Rye. From High Bank Distillery. Drinks like a Barrel Proof Rye.
